# Python Package Mirror Configuration
# Choose your preferred mirror source by uncommenting the corresponding section

# =============================================================================
# China Mirrors (中国镜像源) - Recommended for users in China
# =============================================================================

# Tsinghua University (清华大学) - Default, fast and stable
UV_INDEX_URL=https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple
UV_EXTRA_INDEX_URL=https://pypi.org/simple

# Alibaba Cloud (阿里云) - Alternative option
# UV_INDEX_URL=https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple
# UV_EXTRA_INDEX_URL=https://pypi.org/simple

# Tencent Cloud (腾讯云) - Alternative option
# UV_INDEX_URL=https://mirrors.cloud.tencent.com/pypi/simple
# UV_EXTRA_INDEX_URL=https://pypi.org/simple

# Douban (豆瓣) - Alternative option
# UV_INDEX_URL=https://pypi.douban.com/simple
# UV_EXTRA_INDEX_URL=https://pypi.org/simple

# =============================================================================
# Global Mirrors (全球镜像源) - For users outside China
# =============================================================================

# Official PyPI (官方源) - Default for international users
# UV_INDEX_URL=https://pypi.org/simple
# UV_EXTRA_INDEX_URL=

# =============================================================================
# Usage Instructions (使用说明)
# =============================================================================
# 1. Uncomment your preferred mirror configuration above
# 2. Use with Docker: docker-compose --env-file docker/mirrors.env up
# 3. Or source in shell: source docker/mirrors.env && ./docker/deploy.sh up
# 
# Note: The Dockerfile already includes Tsinghua mirror as default for better
# connectivity in China. You can override it using this file.
